<codeline></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">During<sp/>`TypedCommandBuffer::flush()`,<sp/>each<sp/>command<sp/>type<sp/>is<sp/>processed<sp/>in<sp/>template<sp/>parameter<sp/>order:</highlight></codeline>
